items.sentence: I bet that Tom won't go to Australia next summer.
How long do you think Tom will stay in Australia?
Everybody here except Tom has lived in Australia.
Everyone knew Tom didn't want to visit Australia.
Everyone knew Tom didn't like going to Australia.
Does Tom think that he'll stay in Australia long?
Do you think Tom will be in Australia all summer?
Do you think that Tom wants to live in Australia?
I hear that Tom really likes living in Australia.
I don't think that Tom knows anyone in Australia.
